{"tid":1488330,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"長實擬斥252億　購英釀酒廠及酒館營運商","createTime":"2019-08-19T14:58:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T14:40:57.000Z","uid":14918,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"1c2be90aa674f573ee222417037b307e2042fb1c","tid":1488330,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:58:58.000Z","msg":"長江實業(01113)公布，擬收購在倫敦證交所上市的GREENE KING PLC全部已發行股本及將予發行股本。 <br />\n<br />\n根據收購事項的條款，於協議安排生效後，股東將獲支付現金代價每股股份850便士(約80.8港元)，總現金代價約27億英鎊(約252億港元)。 <br />\n<br />\nGREENE KING為英國具領導地位的釀酒廠及英式酒館營運商，於英格蘭、威爾斯及蘇格蘭等地經營超過2,700間英式酒館、餐廳及酒店，其三個主要業務分支為「Pub Company(英式酒館公司)」、「Pub Partners(英式酒館合作夥伴)」及「Brewing &amp; Brands(釀酒及品牌)」。 <br />\n<br />\n截至今年4月28八日，其擁有1,687家由其經營的英式酒館、餐廳及酒店。"},{"pid":"da87f961b1eccbe2f8a11cd7146f3f25ac3a0edb","tid":1488330,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:59:31.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7d279414721c1842413345da3f672ee258613bb0","tid":1488330,"uid":206827,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:00:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">阻阻大家 入黎擺低死線唔該<br />\n既然無死線做唔到野就擺低死線既日期出黎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家個個話要死線 死線呢？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1488086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1488086</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"927165987e7c752dd22db64c375d785e1e37a802","tid":1488330,"uid":102701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:01:56.000Z","msg":"爆升?"},{"pid":"1ca401af39922fd5cb1deccf4a05115ff5b644f0","tid":1488330,"uid":46587,"like":37,"dislike":2,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:02:45.000Z","msg":"BN